er_column col-xs-12 col-sm-12\"></div>__N__          </div>__N__          <div class=\"row\">__N__            <!-- include lefet sidebar container -->           __N__            <?php includeContainer(\'sidebar\'); ?>__N____N__            <div id=\"center_column\" class=\"center_column col-xs-12 col-sm-9\">__N__              <div class=\"clearfix\">__N__                <section id=\"Legal_notice_section\" contenteditable=\"true\">__N__				    <div class=\"rte\">__N__                	<h2>About us - Privacy Policy</h2>__N__                	<p><span>Last updated: 2024-03-09</span></p>__N__                	<h3>Introduction</h3>__N__                	<p>The Dolibarr association offers the DoliStore platform to help seller and buyer to meet each other. Only the__N__                		service to provide visibility of sold products is offered by the foundation. The foundation does not guarantee__N__                		anything about the quality of the products bought by the customer.</p>__N__                	<p>The DOLIBARR association, via DOLISTORE, collects on behalf of&nbsp;authors/publishers payments for goods sold__N__                		and manages the payment of funds due to them. As such, the association acts under cover of the exemption from__N__                		payment institution approval provided for in Article L521-3 I 2° of the Monetary and Financial Code.</p>__N__                	<h3>The Dolibarr foundation</h3>__N__                	<p>The Dolibarr foundation is a&nbsp;french foundation (Loi 1901) created to help to promote and develop the__N__                		Dolibarr ERP and CRM Open Source software.</p>__N__                	<p>&nbsp;Legal information about the foundation:</p>__N__                	<ul>__N__                		<li>WALDEC&nbsp;: W452006878</li>__N__                		<li>SIREN: 52033993800018</li>__N__                		<li>NAF: 9499Z</li>__N__                	</ul>__N__                	<p>More informations on page&nbsp;<a href=\"https://asso.dolibarr.org/index.php/Dolibarr_foundation\"__N__                			target=\"_blank\">https://asso.dolibarr.org/index.php/Dolibarr_foundation</a></p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h3>Web hosting provider</h3>__N__                	<p>This web site is hosted by OVH, 2 rue Kellermann - 59100 Roubaix - France</p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>__N__                	<p>We may collect the following types of information when you use our DoliStore:</p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<ul>__N__                		<li><strong>Information provided by the user</strong>:<br>DoliStore&nbsp;collect your name, address, VAT number__N__                			and email and password of the account. We also save the list of modules you bought on the platform with the__N__                			price.<br><br></li>__N__                		<li><strong>Information collected automatically</strong>:<br>DoliStore uses Matomo for its statistic tool. No__N__                			private data are collected (even your IP address is anonymized.</li>__N__                	</ul>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>__N__                	<p>The collected informations are used for billing purpose.</p>__N__                	<ul>__N__                		<li>This information is stored into our database.</li>__N__                		<li>You can edit this information for your account</li>__N__                	</ul>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>3. Sharing of Information</h2>__N__                	<ul>__N__                		<li>No data is shared with any other third-parties. Only the members of the board team of the Dolibarr__N__                			foundation, having access to the back-office, have access to the collected information.</li>__N__                	</ul>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>4. Data Security</h2>__N__                	<p>We take reasonable measures to protect information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or__N__                		destruction. The password of accounts are stored using a non reversible hash into the database.&nbsp;</p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>__N__                	<p>You have the right to access, amend, or delete your personal information held by the website.See section \"Contact__N__                		us\" for this.</p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>6. Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>__N__                	<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy__N__                		Policy on this page.</p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                	<h2>7. Contact Us</h2>__N__                	<p>The Data Protection Owner (DPO) in the sens of the GDPR law is the <strong>President of the Dolibarr__N__                			foundation</strong>. You should find its name on this page:&nbsp;<a__N__                			href=\"https://wiki.dolibarr.org/index.php/Office_and_Board_Members\">https://wiki.dolibarr.org/index.php/Office_and_Board_Members</a>__N__                	</p>__N__                	<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us__N__                		at:&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>dolistore@dolibarr.org</b></p>__N__                	<p></p>__N__                </div>__N__				</section>__N____N__              </div>__N__            </div>__N__          </div>__N__        </div>__N__      </div>__N__      <!-- .columns-container -->__N__      <div class=\"footer-container\">__N__        <?php includeContainer(\'footer\'); ?>__N__      </div>__N__    </div>__N__  </body>__N__</html>', '', 0);

